{"type": "article", "id": 5344, "title": "ORA Unika 手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-19T07:57:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 41, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233736UdtwPNpcKER3Giqx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Denis Guidone 为意大利品牌 NAVA Design 设计了一款名为「ORA Unika」的手表，一眼看过去会以为设计师想要故意模糊时间的概念，但静下来再仔细看却能发现设计师的巧思与趣味。在其简洁的黑色圆形表盘上，Denis Guidone 将常规的时针与分针进行再创作，变成了看似随性画出的弯曲线条，较长的一端表示时针，较短的一端表示分针。如此任性的表盘也许只是想让你多看看它呢。定价 91.67 英镑（约合人民币 862 元），<a href=\"http://www.dezeenwatchstore.com/shop/denis-guidone-ora-unica/\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233732SZe7NnQqvG39mcRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233733mqgIDy8OJUPdhib0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233733kpt6UMRFTjD7OW4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233734bufCBmXUNj6aVk4d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.790625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233734cExkmjeFTqySwUDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052337349UPiXYkSd5RAbwuH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}